OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,FAn Army veteran has called on people
OL,7,Fto remember those who served in lesser-
OL,8,Fknown conflicts, and not just to focus
OL,9,Fon "the big wars".
OL,11,FDuring his 25 years in the Army, Derek
OL,12,F"Benny" Bennett saw active service in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland at the height of the
OL,14,FTroubles, served in a peacekeeping
OL,15,Fmission in Cyprus, and as a liaison
OL,16,Fofficer in the Gulf War.
