OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,FThe 72-year-old, who left the Army in
OL,7,F1992, said the "scars" people got from
OL,8,Fserving in "less talked-about places"
OL,9,Fare just as real as those from well-
OL,10,Fknown conflicts, and that they deserve
OL,11,Fthe same respect.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of Remembrance Day, he
OL,14,Fsaid: "It's crucial we remember not
OL,15,Fjust the big wars like the Second
OL,16,FWorld War, the Falklands, Afghanistan,
OL,17,For Iraq, but all the conflicts and
OL,18,Fpeacekeeping missions that don't
OL,19,Falways make the headlines.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@VO]pD@LOUpD@eO]vD@GOU
