OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,F"I know people who have suffered, and
OL,7,FI personally know that the scars `
OL,8,Fwhether seen or unseen ` are just as
OL,9,Freal for those who served in less
OL,10,Ftalked-about places.
OL,12,F"The impact on those who were there is
OL,13,Fthe same, and their sacrifices deserve
OL,14,Fthe same respect and remembrance."
OL,16,FThe veteran, originally from Shotton
OL,17,Fin North Wales and who now lives in a
OL,18,Fhome in Edinburgh run by veterans'
OL,19,Fcharity Erskine, recalled some of his
OL,20,Fown military experiences.
