OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,FThese included one particularly close
OL,7,Fcall while he was serving with the
OL,8,FParachute Regiment (Paras) in Northern
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,F"A rocket fired by an RPG-7 missed our
OL,12,Fvehicle by just six inches ` we were
OL,13,Fvery lucky," he said.
OL,15,F"You'd be lying if you said you
OL,16,Fweren't scared. We were backing up the
OL,17,Finfantry, and you could feel the
OL,18,Ftension in the air.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@LO]wD@AOU
