OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,F"The fear was always there, but you
OL,7,Fjust had to push it down and get on
OL,8,Fwith the job.
OL,10,F"There were some dark days, but amidst
OL,11,Fit all I met some wonderful people."
OL,13,FSergeant Major Bennett was also with
OL,14,Fthe Paras on the ground in Cyprus in
OL,15,F1974, when the Turkish invasion
OL,16,Funfolded, and he spent six months as
OL,17,Fpart of the UN peacekeeping force.
