OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,F"I loved every minute of it; that was
OL,7,Fthe best three years of my Army
OL,8,Fcareer," he said of his time with the
OL,9,Fregiment.
OL,11,FIn 1989 he was deployed to Tel Aviv in
OL,12,FIsrael, where he served as a liaison
OL,13,Fofficer with the multinational force
OL,14,Fand observers (MFO) during the first
OL,15,FGulf War.
OL,17,FThis role saw him responsible,
OL,18,Falongside a Dutch major, for trying to
OL,19,Fensure the safety of staff and MFO
OL,20,Fpersonnel amid a barrage of Scud
OL,21,Fmissile attacks.
