OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,FDespite suffering a serious spinal
OL,7,Fcord injury in 2018 that left him
OL,8,Fparalysed, the veteran remains active
OL,9,Fand driven, and maintains a daily
OL,10,Ffitness routine at the Erskine home.
OL,12,F"Erskine is a great place to be and
OL,13,Fthe staff are brilliant," he said.
OL,15,F"They do a fantastic job. The staff at
OL,16,FErskine honour veterans of all ages
OL,17,Fevery single day with their care and
OL,18,Fdedication.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@YO]wD@AOU
