OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,F"It's not just about remembering our
OL,7,Fservice; it's about making sure we
OL,8,Ffeel valued, respected, and looked
OL,9,Fafter, no matter what we've been
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,12,F"They really go above and beyond, and
OL,13,FI couldn't ask for a better place to
OL,14,Fbe."
OL,16,FWing Commander Ian Cumming, chief
OL,17,Fexecutive of Erskine Veterans Charity,
OL,18,Fsaid: "Erskine, as Scotland's leading
OL,19,Fveterans charity, is committed to
OL,20,Fhonouring veterans like Benny who have
OL,21,Fgiven so much for their country.
