OL,3,CPause to remember all conflicts and
OL,4,Cnot just the 'big wars', says veteran
OL,6,F"Our staff work tirelessly every day
OL,7,Fto provide the highest standard of
OL,8,Fcare, accommodation and community
OL,9,Fsupport, to ensure that all our
OL,10,Fveterans feel valued and respected.
OL,12,F"This Remembrance Day, we will come
OL,13,Ftogether as a charity to pay tribute
OL,14,Fto veterans of all ages and from all
OL,15,Fconflicts, reflecting on their immense
OL,16,Fcontributions and sacrifices.
OL,18,F"It's our mission to make sure their
OL,19,Flegacies are never forgotten, and we
OL,20,Fare proud to be a part of their
OL,21,Fjourney."
